      <title>[碎念] mdadm 超級慢的rebuild 速度 Incredibly Slow mdadm Rebuild</title>
      <link>https://blog.cowbay.org/p/%E7%A2%8E%E5%BF%B5-mdadm-%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E6%85%A2%E7%9A%84rebuild-%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6-incredibly-slow-mdadm-rebuild/</link>
